    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in naturally aspirated precision, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a flawless VANOS system. The chassis is structurally immaculate, benefiting from preventative subframe reinforcement and a crisp-shifting Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Every component, from the M-Variable differential to the factory-spec dampers, operates with showroom-level mechanical integrity. Finished in original Carbon Black with a pristine Nappa interior, this example offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector.",
